messages.content: Hello! I'm here and ready to assist you. How can I help you today?
I want to know my bank account.
Of course! Could you please provide me with your account number so I can assist you with your balance inquiry?

The text may contain account numbers in format XXXXX-XXXXXX or XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
Of course, I'm here to help with your banking needs. If you have a specific query or need information on your account, feel free to let me know!
